{"id":42,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":42,"title":"D&C 38","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 38"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Fayette, New York, January 2, 1831. The occasion was a conference of the Church."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.1-6"},"1–6"],", Christ created all things;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.7-8"},"7–8"],", He is in the midst of His Saints, who will soon see Him;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.9-12"},"9–12"],", All flesh is corrupted before Him;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.13-22"},"13–22"],", He has reserved a land of promise for His Saints in time and in eternity;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.23-27"},"23–27"],", The Saints are commanded to be one and esteem each other as brethren;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.28-29"},"28–29"],", Wars are predicted;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.30-33"},"30–33"],", The Saints are to be given power from on high and to go forth among all nations;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.34-42"},"34–42"],", The Church is commanded to care for the poor and needy and to seek the riches of eternity."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.1","order":"06.05.038.4351"},["b","1"],"Thus saith the Lord your God, even Jesus Christ, the Great",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"I Am"]],", Alpha and Omega, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"beginning"],"and the end, the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"same"],"which looked upon the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"wide"],"expanse of eternity, and all the seraphic",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"hosts"],"of heaven,",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_1f"},"before"],"the world was",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_1g"},"made"],";"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.2","order":"06.05.038.4352"},["b","2"],"The same which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"knoweth"],"all things, for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"all"],"things are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"present"],"before mine eyes;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.3","order":"06.05.038.4353"},["b","3"],"I am the same which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"spake"],", and the world was made, and all things came by me."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.4","order":"06.05.038.4354"},["b","4"],"I am the same which have taken the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Zion"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"Enoch"],"into mine own bosom; and verily, I say, even as many as have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"believed"],"in my name, for I am Christ, and in mine own name, by the virtue of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"blood"],"which I have spilt, have I pleaded before the Father for them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.5","order":"06.05.038.4355"},["b","5"],"But behold, the residue of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wicked"],"have I kept in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"chains"],"of darkness until the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"judgment"],"of the great day, which shall come at the end of the earth;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.6","order":"06.05.038.4356"},["b","6"],"And even so will I cause the wicked to be kept, that will not hear my voice but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"harden"],"their hearts, and wo, wo, wo, is their doom."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.7","order":"06.05.038.4357"},["b","7"],"But behold, verily, verily, I say unto you that mine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"eyes"],"are upon you. I am in your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"midst"],"and ye cannot",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"see"],"me;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.8","order":"06.05.038.4358"},["b","8"],"But the day soon cometh that ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"see"],"me, and know that I am; for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"veil"],"of darkness shall soon be rent, and he that is not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"purified"],"shall not",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"abide"],"the day."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.9","order":"06.05.038.4359"},["b","9"],"Wherefore, gird up your loins and be prepared. Behold, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"kingdom"],"is yours, and the enemy shall not overcome."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.10","order":"06.05.038.4360"},["b","10"],"Verily I say unto you, ye are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"clean"],", but not all; and there is none else with whom I am well",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"pleased"],";"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.11","order":"06.05.038.4361"},["b","11"],"For all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"flesh"],"is corrupted before me; and the powers of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"darkness"],"prevail upon the earth, among the children of men, in the presence of all the hosts of heaven—"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.12","order":"06.05.038.4362"},["b","12"],"Which causeth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"silence"],"to reign, and all eternity is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"pained"],", and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"angels"],"are waiting the great command to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"reap"],"down the earth, to",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_12e"},"gather"],"the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_12f"},"tares"],"that they may be",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_12g"},"burned"],"; and, behold, the enemy is combined."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.13","order":"06.05.038.4363"},["b","13"],"And now I show unto you a mystery, a thing which is had in secret chambers, to bring to pass even your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"destruction"],"in process of time, and ye knew it not;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.14","order":"06.05.038.4364"},["b","14"],"But now I tell it unto you, and ye are blessed, not because of your iniquity, neither your hearts of unbelief; for verily some of you are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"guilty"],"before me, but I will be merciful unto your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"weakness"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.15","order":"06.05.038.4365"},["b","15"],"Therefore, be ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"strong"],"from henceforth;",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"fear not"],", for the kingdom is yours."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.16","order":"06.05.038.4366"},["b","16"],"And for your salvation I give unto you a commandment, for I have heard your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"prayers"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"poor"],"have complained before me, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"rich"],"have I made, and all flesh is mine, and I am no",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"respecter"],"of persons."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.17","order":"06.05.038.4367"},["b","17"],"And I have made the earth rich, and behold it is my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"footstool"],", wherefore, again I will stand upon it."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.18","order":"06.05.038.4368"},["b","18"],"And I hold forth and deign to give unto you greater riches, even a land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"promise"],", a land",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"flowing"],"with milk and honey, upon which there shall be no",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"curse"],"when the Lord cometh;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.19","order":"06.05.038.4369"},["b","19"],"And I will give it unto you for the land of your inheritance, if you seek it with all your hearts."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.20","order":"06.05.038.4370"},["b","20"],"And this shall be my covenant with you, ye shall have it for the land of your inheritance, and for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"inheritance"],"of your children forever, while the earth shall stand, and ye shall possess it again in eternity, no more to pass away."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.21","order":"06.05.038.4371"},["b","21"],"But, verily I say unto you that in time ye shall have no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"king"],"nor ruler, for I will be your king and watch over you."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.22","order":"06.05.038.4372"},["b","22"],"Wherefore, hear my voice and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"follow"],"me, and you shall be a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"free"],"people, and ye shall have no laws but my laws when I come, for I am your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"lawgiver"],", and what can stay my hand?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.23","order":"06.05.038.4373"},["b","23"],"But, verily I say unto you,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"teach"],"one another according to the office wherewith I have appointed you;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.24","order":"06.05.038.4374"},["b","24"],"And let every man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"esteem"],"his brother as himself, and practice",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"virtue"],"and holiness before me."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.25","order":"06.05.038.4375"},["b","25"],"And again I say unto you, let every man esteem his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"brother"],"as himself."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.26","order":"06.05.038.4376"},["b","26"],"For what man among you having twelve sons, and is no respecter of them, and they serve him obediently, and he saith unto the one: Be thou clothed in robes and sit thou here; and to the other: Be thou clothed in rags and sit thou there—and looketh upon his sons and saith I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"just"],"?"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.27","order":"06.05.038.4377"},["b","27"],"Behold, this I have given unto you as a parable, and it is even as I am. I say unto you, be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"one"],"; and if ye are not one ye are not mine."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.28","order":"06.05.038.4378"},["b","28"],"And again, I say unto you that the enemy in the secret chambers seeketh your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"lives"],"."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.29","order":"06.05.038.4379"},["b","29"],"Ye hear of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"wars"],"in far countries, and you say that there will soon be great wars in far countries, but ye know not the hearts of men in your own land."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.30","order":"06.05.038.4380"},["b","30"],"I tell you these things because of your prayers; wherefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"treasure"],"up",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"wisdom"],"in your bosoms, lest the wickedness of men reveal these things unto you by their wickedness, in a manner which shall speak in your ears with a voice louder than that which shall shake the earth; but if ye are prepared ye shall not fear."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.31","order":"06.05.038.4381"},["b","31"],"And that ye might escape the power of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"enemy"],", and be gathered unto me a righteous people, without",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"spot"],"and blameless—"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.32","order":"06.05.038.4382"},["b","32"],"Wherefore, for this cause I gave unto you the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"commandment"],"that ye should go to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"Ohio"],"; and there I will give unto you my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_32c"},"law"],"; and there you shall be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_32d"},"endowed"],"with power from on high;"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.33","order":"06.05.038.4383"},["b","33"],"And from thence, whosoever I will shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"go forth"],"among all nations, and it shall be told them what they shall do; for I have a great work laid up in store, for Israel shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"saved"],", and I will",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_33c"},"lead"],"them whithersoever I will, and no power shall",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_33d"},"stay"],"my hand."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.34","order":"06.05.038.4384"},["b","34"],"And now, I give unto the church in these parts a commandment, that certain men among them shall be appointed, and they shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"appointed"],"by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"voice"],"of the church;"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.35","order":"06.05.038.4385"},["b","35"],"And they shall look to the poor and the needy, and administer to their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"relief"],"that they shall not suffer; and send them forth to the place which I have commanded them;"],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.36","order":"06.05.038.4386"},["b","36"],"And this shall be their work, to govern the affairs of the property of this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"church"],"."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.37","order":"06.05.038.4387"},["b","37"],"And they that have farms that cannot be sold, let them be left or rented as seemeth them good."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.38","order":"06.05.038.4388"},["b","38"],"See that all things are preserved; and when men are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"endowed"],"with power from on high and sent forth, all these things shall be gathered unto the bosom of the church."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.39","order":"06.05.038.4389"},["b","39"],"And if ye seek the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"riches"],"which it is the will of the Father to give unto you, ye shall be the richest of all people, for ye shall have the riches of eternity; and it must needs be that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"riches"],"of the earth are mine to give; but beware of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_39c"},"pride"],", lest ye become as the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_39d"},"Nephites"],"of old."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.40","order":"06.05.038.4390"},["b","40"],"And again, I say unto you, I give unto you a commandment, that every man, both elder, priest, teacher, and also member, go to with his might, with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"labor"],"of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_40b"},"hands"],", to prepare and accomplish the things which I have commanded."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.41","order":"06.05.038.4391"},["b","41"],"And let your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"preaching"],"be the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_41b"},"warning"],"voice, every man to his neighbor, in mildness and in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_41c"},"meekness"],"."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.42","order":"06.05.038.4392"},["b","42"],"And go ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"out"],"from among the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_42b"},"wicked"],". Save yourselves. Be ye",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_42c"},"clean"],"that bear the vessels of the Lord. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptu